      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DR. NAKITA (2) hit the ground running from out wide and on speed early but faded and swamped late when 7th at Sandown in Maiden FIN company. Ready to return to form. ASTON NEWSON (8) is a Jacqueline Berry-trained newcomer by Aston Exceed out of Aston Geneve. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Market moves likely to signal ability but profiles strongly for this. DEEP TALENT (7) has an honest record despite remaining a maiden and overdue for a win, having placed 12 of 24 career runs. Has hit the frame at the last six starts. Likely to be in the finish again. LOUIE LOUIE (3) makes debut for the Matthew Clark kennel. Profiles well so watch market closely.",
